{"tid":321652,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"東京川越唔坐巴士 用腳行會唔會行到腳斷？","createTime":"2017-07-14T10:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T11:27:38.000Z","uid":1533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"12a91ecf8109d970ac8cf485a276f9771cd38453","tid":321652,"uid":1533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:05:34.000Z","msg":"第一次去，想試下就咁慢慢行<br />\n景點與景點之間其實遠唔遠？<br />\n見好多人介紹都係坐巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2720446d7cd8553b5424caccf424c96d3d8162d","tid":321652,"uid":20260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:08:32.000Z","msg":"睇地圖好似好大 但其實成個川越市好細<br />\n慢慢行仲嘆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6833af5acd8d0b4bc510e605b2db005ef0ba79","tid":321652,"uid":50322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:08:33.000Z","msg":"由 jr 到主要景點 係遠架 <br />\n最好買拉 <br />\n<br />\n但 中間 景點之間 就近 可步行 去到"},{"pid":"174b7782d5d0e7897816483dc4830e9f541c670c","tid":321652,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:09:25.000Z","msg":"來回要坐 景點area唔洗<br />\n來回唔坐就每程行半個鐘 你接受到就ok"},{"pid":"434bff759493ac461ae8c05d1d5ca7a74e25a3ab","tid":321652,"uid":19025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:10:44.000Z","msg":"川越腳行得架喇<br />\n啲鋪頭幾有特色 值得用大半日行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1fd0306d57c4b7c0feab956e77ed92933592d4","tid":321652,"uid":47338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:33:21.000Z","msg":"睇你借唔借和服，同埋行邊幾個景點<br />\n你唔急還衫可以行，時の鐘同一番街果邊<br />\n喜多院同冰川神社果啲你都係搭車啦<br />\nshuttlebus有哂時間表，自己安排"},{"pid":"119d6137da31bd56766effba98c5629a86890160","tid":321652,"uid":1533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:09:36.000Z","msg":"唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923d817e4eb5b1256d2234e85dd5c7ad42f4d3c4","tid":321652,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:27:38.000Z","msg":"嗰時去淨係去冰川神社同埋小江戶<br />\n由川越站一直慢慢行，行過小江戶再去冰川<br />\n半個鐘內到冰川<br />\n其實唔趕景點慢慢行下幾好"}]}